  <description><![CDATA[<p>This apartment along with its neighbouring <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/{localLink:437a515c-bac3-4924-bfc1-ffbf5850b906}" target="_blank" title="Villa Bella Vista Mountain Chalet Apartments"><strong>Bella Vista</strong></a>, are located in pretty mountain chalets in the popular “Petit Village” area of Zermatt. Beautifully furnished, they offer high standards of comfort with modern amenities and are ideal for families and groups of friends. The A La Casa and the <a rel="noopener noreferrer" href="/{localLink:437a515c-bac3-4924-bfc1-ffbf5850b906}" target="_blank" title="Villa Bella Vista Mountain Chalet Apartments"><strong>Bella Vista</strong></a> are generally booked independently of each other, but would also ideally suit two families travelling together, but wanting their own separate ‘home from home’.</p>
<p>In an elevated position with sensational views across Zermatt to the iconic Matterhorn, the chalet apartments are reached with ease by a small funicular-style lift from resort level. The resort centre and supermarket are approximately 8-10 minutes’ walk away.</p>]]></description>
