  <roomsDescription><![CDATA[<ul>
<li>Sleeps 4-8, in four Continental twin bedrooms (on two floors)</li>
<li><strong>Upper Floor:</strong> Entrance to apartment; open-plan spacious living/dining area with exposed wooden beams, south-facing balcony with superb views over Zermatt; fully-equipped kitchen; balcony and hot-tub on the terrace, accessed through Bedroom 1, which has private adjacent shower/wc and new sauna.</li>
<li><strong>Lower Floor:</strong> Three further bedrooms, all with patio access Bedroom 2 with en suite bath/wc, and Bedrooms 3 &amp; 4 sharing adjacent bath/wc.</li>
</ul>]]></roomsDescription>
